---
// Features.astro
---
<section class="features" id="why-us">
  <div class="container features-container">
    <div class="features-content fade-in">
      <p class="section-label">La diferencia de Tu Diseño ideal</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">¿Por qué <em>elegirnos</em>?</h2>
      <div class="features-list">
        <div class="feature-item fade-in d-1">
          <div class="feature-bullet">1</div>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h4>Diseño 100% Personalizado</h4>
            <p>No usamos moldes genéricos. Cada proyecto se dibuja, talla y conceptualiza según tu visión.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item fade-in d-2">
          <div class="feature-bullet">2</div>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h4>Atención Detallada</h4>
            <p>Desde el primer boceto hasta el montaje final, cuidamos cada textura, color y proporción.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item fade-in d-3">
          <div class="feature-bullet">3</div>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <h4>Materiales de Alta Gama</h4>
            <p>Trabajamos con resina de calidad premium, globos duraderos y styrofoam de alta densidad para acabados perfectos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="features-visual fade-in d-2">
      <div class="image-stack">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544457070-4cd773b4d71e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" 
          alt="Detalle de resina y oro" 
          class="img-back"
        />
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1530103862676-de8c9debad1d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" 
          alt="Globos decorativos en evento" 
          class="img-front"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.features {
  background: var(--color-surface);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.features::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 50%;
  background: var(--color-bg);
  z-index: 0;
}

.features-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.features-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2rem;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}

.feature-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.feature-bullet {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  background: var(--color-accent-dim);
  color: var(--color-accent-dark);
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-accent);
}

.feature-text h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  color: var(--color-heading);
  font-size: var(--size-lg);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  font-weight: 400;
}

.feature-text p {
  color: var(--color-text);
  font-size: var(--size-sm);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* -- Visual -- */
.features-visual {
  position: relative;
  height: 500px;
}

.image-stack {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.img-back {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  width: 75%;
  height: 80%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.img-front {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 65%;
  height: 70%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  border: 10px solid var(--color-surface);
  box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .features-container {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  .features-visual {
    height: 400px;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }
}
</style>
